Remove Element:

Link : https://leetcode.com/problems/remove-element/description/

Implementation:

class Solution {
    public int removeElement(int[] arr, int val) {
        int c=0;
        for(int i=0;i<arr.length;i++){
            if(val!=arr[i]){
                arr[c]=arr[i];
                c++;
            }
        }
        return c;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(n)
Space Complexity : O(1)
